body.description: Centrum Multivitamin for Women is a complete multivitamin/multimineral supplement formulated with B Vitamins to help support energy and metabolism and Antioxidant Vitamins C and E to support immunity (1). This multivitamin with iron for women contains 23 key micronutrients and other important nutrients to help support your body head-to-toe (1). These vitamin supplements contain B Vitamins to help support energy and assist the metabolism of macronutrients, Antioxidant Vitamins C and E for immune support, and biotin and Vitamins A, C and E to help maintain a healthy appearance (1). Each women's multivitamin with iron contains 100 percent or more of the daily value of iron, biotin and Vitamin D3, Vitamin B6 and Vitamin B12, as well as Vitamin A and Vitamin E. Centrum women's vitamin tablets are Non-GMO (2) and gluten free to meet a variety of dietary needs. With 250 tablets per bottle, it's easy to maintain your health by taking one women's daily multivitamin tablet with food. (1) These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease. (2) Non-GMO applies to Centrum and Centrum Silver tablets only; learn more at Centrum's official website

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Diseñado específicamente para satisfacer las necesidades nutricionales de las mujeres
reviews.reviewText: Centrum Women es un suplemento vitamínico y mineral diseñado específicamente para satisfacer las necesidades nutricionales de las mujeres. Permíteme proporcionarte una revisión basada en información real:Ingredientes Clave: Centrum Women contiene una combinación de ingredientes clave que favorecen la salud y el bienestar femenino. Estos incluyen vitaminas y minerales esenciales como las vitaminas B, calcio, hierro y ácido fólico. Estos nutrientes son importantes para la salud ósea, la función cognitiva, la energía y la salud cardiovascular1.Producción y Distribución: Centrum Women es producido y distribuido por Pfizer, una de las corporaciones farmacéuticas más grandes del mundo. A nivel mundial, Pfizer comercializa fórmulas de Centrum especializadas para distintos grupos etarios.Fortalezas y Debilidades:Fortalezas: Se destacan su precio asequible, envase atractivo y el hecho de ser fabricado por un reconocido fabricante.Debilidades: Sin embargo, algunas debilidades incluyen su baja efectividad debido al uso de componentes sintéticos de “limitada biodisponibilidad” o absorción.Cantidad Recomendada: La cantidad recomendada de cada vitamina y mineral incluidos en las variantes del multivitamínico Centrum está diseñada para apoyar al grupo de edad y sexo para el cual se formula1.En resumen, si buscas un suplemento vitamínico diseñado especialmente para mujeres, Centrum Women podría ser una buena elección para cubrir tus necesidades nutricionales.

reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars These vitamins messed up my sleep cycle
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this because the older I get the more I need to balance out my body. I also frequently feel like I have no energy during the day.The first thing I noticed is that this brand has Red 40 dye, which I did not see when I looked at the ingredient list on Amazon.The second thing I noticed after only taking a few days, is that my sleep cycle became terribly messed up. I couldn't fall asleep until after midnight, and even after stopping the vitamins, it took several weeks until my sleep cycle got back on track. This was the only thing I changed during that time, so I don't know what else could have affected it.Based on those 2 issues, I cannot recommend these vitamins.
